lead_paragraph: A Bolivian spectator was killed at the Dakar Rally on Saturday when he was hit by a Mitsubishi driven by Frenchman Lionel Baud during the seventh stage from Bolivia to Argentina, organizers said.

headline.print_headline: Spectator Killed During Dakar Rally in Bolivia
